node.text:
Coached by @Crystalrose.Sanders, these skaters aged 8-20 and leveled from preliminary to senior, show that skating is all about perseverance and hard work, no matter how hard things may get. Keep your head up, stay motivated and don't let anyone stop you from your goals and dreams.

Good luck to all the skaters at National Showcase this week!!!

🎥 by Jordan @oniceperspectives

node.text:
It’s hard to believe I was off the ice for over four weeks, so I was grateful to have a “warm up” with Ash while visiting @the.cains down in Dallas. 💪
❄️
__⛸ Ashley Cain-Gribble
__🏋️ Derek Valiska @dvaliska
__📍 Zero Limits Performance
__🎥 Jordan @oniceperspectives
❄️

node.text:
Wishing @ka2sh a happy launch of @openicecollective’s new film ‘VISIONARIES’, now available to stream for a limited time on openicecollective.com.

“I Feel the Earth Move” was filmed previously for @icetheatreofny’s spring fundraiser “Pivoting Through the Pandemic”. Learn more at icetheatre.org.

__⛸ Kaitlyn Weaver @ka2sh
__🎥 Filmed by Jordan @oniceperspectives
__🎵 I Feel the Earth Move @carole_king

node.text:
Mariah: “So honored to have worked with @denalifoxx for this years short program!! Thank you for creating this program and for helping me understand the history and importance of the movement! 💖💃🏻💖 And…..Thank you so much @oniceperspectives for capturing this snippet!!”
❄️

node.text:
2021 US Novice Men’s Champion Beck Strommer self-choreographed this piece just to be filmed during my visit to the Springs a couple weeks ago. Congrats Beck on being named to @usfigureskating’s International Selection Pool!
__⛸ @beck_s_sk8s
__🎥 Jordan @oniceperspectives
__🎵 Lovely @billieeilish

node.text:
“Chopinesque” starring @jo___joe, from the American Contemporary Skating Festival Exhibition in Boston, MA. Enjoy the full video on YouTube.com/OnIcePerspectives

Choreographer @mcswain_kate: “We created modern dance inspired movements, angles, and shapes and included some playfulness in the movement too. The piece of music is a jazzy take on a classical piece so we echoed that sentiment in the choreography.”

Special Thanks to @AmericanIceTheatre

⛸ Joey Millet @jo___joe @coachjoeymillet
🎥 by Jordan @oniceperspectives
🎵 Chopinesque - @JonBatiste
📍 @WarriorIceArena

node.text:
Coached by @Crystalrose.Sanders, these skaters aged 8-20 and leveled from preliminary to senior, show that skating is all about perseverance and hard work, no matter how hard things may get. Keep your head up, stay motivated and don't let anyone stop you from your goals and dreams.

Good luck to all the skaters at National Showcase this week!!!

🎥 by Jordan @oniceperspectives
